rComments: great prof overall!! bello is very caring and approachable. her term test is easy but the quizzes and the final were brutal. even when you don't understand the concept just memorize it word by word from the slides and practice and you'll be fine. definitely recommend but get ready to memorize ALL HER SLIDES.
teacherRatingTags: ['Accessible outside class', "Skip class? You won't pass."]

rComments: I found her to be kind of rude. She posts powerpoints on Quercus that aren't filled out, so we have to fill them out during the lecture. This was distracting. Doesn't post answers to homework or filled out powerpoints online.I wish I didn't take this class to be honest.

She is a VERY organized and well structured professor. You will know what to expect and what will happen in class. She has a great system for participation, so that even if you don't like raising your hand in class, there are ways for you to earn participation marks.
